name: The Fishermen Friend
description:
White heron and his Pacific salmon stand, 
It sells well more over after long stormy day, 

For stew , jerky, or sushi
Salted, steak, or Sashimi
Smoked salmon come to me. 

White Heron oo white Heron, all white creature are people of Oberon

Pacific Salmon swam on Winter
If there's an Olympic they'll be the winner
If there's net, all be a fish wiener
